thing about finding places for the two of them as well. Perhaps in the City Watch.\'94 
\par The queen\rquote s smile had frozen so hard she feared her teeth might crack. }{\cs28\i Garth the Gross on the small council and his two bastards in the gold cloaks . . . do the Tyrells think I will just serve the realm up to them on a gilded platter?}{
