Was that some ploy? Could he have been plotting with the Imp all the while, conspiring at Father\rquote s death?}{ With Tywin Lannister in his grave, Lord Tyrell was an obvious choice to be King\rquote s Hand, but even so . . . \'93
You will not speak of this with anyone,\'94 she commanded. 
