\par \'93In my company as well.\'94 The queen put the coin away. She would think about it later. \'93What of the other matter?\'94 
\par \'93Ser Gregor.\'94 Qyburn shrugged. \'93I have examined him, as you commanded. The poison on the Viper\rquote s spear was manticore venom from the east, I would stake my life on that.\'94 
\par \'93Pycelle says no. He told my lord father that manticore venom kills the instant it reaches the heart.\'94 
\par \'93And so it does. But this venom has been }{\cs28\i thickened}{ somehow, so as to draw out the Mountain\rquote s dying.\'94 
