\par \'93You heard me.\'94 
\par \'93I did, my lord, I suredly did, and yet . . . my lord may question who he pleases, \rquote tis true, it is not my place to say that he may not. But, ser, if I may be so bold, I do not think them like to answer. They are dead, my lord.\'94 
