\par \'93Bloodraven?\'94 said Dareon. \'93I know a song about him. \lquote A Thousand Eyes, and One,\rquote  it\rquote s called. But I thought he lived a hundred years ago.\'94 
\par \'93We all did. Once I was as young as you.\'94 That seemed to make him sad. He coughed, and closed his eyes, and went to sleep, swaying in his furs whenever some wave rocked the ship. 
