\par She knocked aside his arm and punched the steel into his bowels. \'93Laugh,\'94 she snarled at him. He moaned instead. \'93Laugh,\'94 she repeated, grabbing his throat with one hand and stabbing at his belly with the other. }{\cs28\i \'93Laugh!\'94}{
