\par \'93I am sorry she is dead,\'94 Myrcella said. 
\par \'93She\rquote s not, sweet queen.\'94 Garin flashed the golden tooth Arianne had bought him to replace the one she\rquote d broken. \'93I\rquote m of the orphans of the Greenblood, is what my lady means.\'94 
