e that much easier for them to bend their knees to Queen Myrcella. And Lord Tywin had been a dangerous foe; without him, Dorne\rquote s enemies would be much weaker. }{\cs28\i Lannisters are killing Lannisters, how sweet.}{ \'93What became of the dwarf?
\'94 
