\par The moon had c
rowned the Moonmaid as they set out from the dust-dry ruins of Shandystone, striking south and west. Arianne and Ser Arys took the lead, with Myrcella on a frisky mare between them. Garin followed close behind with Spotted Sylva, whilst her two Dornish kn
ights took the rear. }{\cs28\i We are seven,}{ Arianne realized as they rode. She had not thought of that before, but it seemed a good omen for their cause. }{\cs28\i Seven riders on their way to glory. One day the singers will make all of us immortal.}{
