\'93I will make a bargain with you. Relieve me of this duty, and my razor is yours to command.\'94 
\par Her mouth tightened. She had been drinking hot spiced wine and smelled of nutmeg. \'93You presume to dicker with me? Need I remind you, you are sworn to obey.\'94 
