. She looked forward to hearing men speak of her father as a \'93she.\'94 Another of the ships would be named }{\cs28\i Sweet Cersei,}{ and would bear a gilded figurehead carved in her likeness, clad in mail and lion helm, with spear in hand. }{\cs28\i 
