\par The }{\cs28\i Iron Victory}{ lingered for hours off the mouth of the Mander. As the greater part of the Iron Fleet got under way for Oakenshield, Victarion kept }{\cs28\i Grief, Lord Dagon, Iron Wind,}{ and }{\cs28\i Maiden\rquote s Bane}{
