\par Septon Meribald smiled. \'93It is called the Hermit\rquote s Hole. The first holy man to find his way here lived therein, and worked such wonders that others came to join him. That was two thousand years ago, they say. The door came somewhat later.\'94 

\par Perhaps two thousand years ago the Hermit\rquote s
