\par }{\cs28\i The horse.}{ She had seen the stallion, had heard it kicking, but she had not understood. Destriers were trained to kick and bite. In war they were a weapon, like the men who rode them. }{\cs28\i Like the Hound.}{ \'93It is true, then,\'94
