der. She gasped some words in a foreign tongue, then shuddered again and arched her back and screamed. }{\cs28\i She sounds as if she is being gored,}{ the queen thought. For a moment she let herself imagine that her fingers were a bore\rquote 
s tusks, ripping the Myrish woman apart from groin to throat. 
\par It was still no good. 
\par It had never been any good with anyone but Jaime. 
\par When she tried to take her hand away, Taena caught it and kissed her fingers. \'93Sweet queen, how shall I pleasure you?\'94 She slid her hand down Cersei\rquote s side and touched her sex. \'93Tell me what you would have of me, my love.\'94 
\par \'93Leave me.\'94 Cersei rolled away and pulled up the bedclothes to cover herself, shivering. Dawn was breaking. It would be morning soon, and all of this would be forgotten. 
\par It had never happened.
