d given her, but the Blackfish was looking at him the way that Eddard Stark had looked at him when he\rquote d found him on the Iron Throne with the Mad King\rquote s blood upon his blade. \'93
I came to speak of the living, not the dead. Of those who need not die, but shall . . .\'94 
