My nephew is marked for death no matter what I do. So hang him and be done with it. I expect that Edmure is as weary of standing on those gallows as I am of seeing him there.\'94 
\par }{\cs28\i Ryman Frey is a bloody fool.}{ His mummer\rquote s show with Edmure and the gallows had only made the Blackfish more obdurate, that was plain. \'93You hold Lady Sybelle Westerling and three of her children. I\rquote 
ll return your nephew in exchange for them.\'94 
\par \'93As you returned Lady Catelyn\rquote s daughters?\'94 
\par Jaime did not allow himself to be provoked. \'93An old woman and three children for your liege lord. That\rquote s a better bargain than you could have hoped for.\'94 
