\par }{\cs28\i Now, there\rquote s an awful prospect.}{ \'93I would have slain Robb Stark in the Whispering Wood, if I could have reached him. Some fools got in my way. Does it matter how the boy perished? He\rquote 
s no less dead, and his kingdom died when he did.\'94 
