reen and grey, spotted with the brown blooms of decay. The flesh of her face clung in ragged strips from her eyes down to her jaw. Some of the rips were crusted with dried blood, but others gaped open to reveal the skull beneath. 
\par }{\cs28\i Her face,}{ Brienne thought. }{\cs28\i Her face was so strong and handsome, her skin so smooth and soft.}{ \'93Lady Catelyn?\'94 Tears filled her eyes. \'93They said . . . they said that you were dead.\'94 
