She says that you must prove your faith.\'94 
\par \'93How?\'94 asked Brienne. 
\par \'93With your sword. }{\cs28\i Oathkeeper,}{ you call it? Then keep your oath to her, milady says.\'94 
\par \'93What does she want of me?\'94 
\par \'93She wants her son alive, or the men who killed him dead,\'94 said the big man. \'93She wants to feed the crows, like they did at the Red Wedding. Freys and Boltons, aye. We\rquote ll giv
