\par \'93Aye. He did that. I have heard many men confess, Your Grace, but seldom have I heard a man so pleased to be so guilty.\'94 
\par \'93You }{\cs28\i whipped}{ him!\'94 
\par \'93There can be no penance without pain. No man should spare himself the scourge, as I told Ser Osney. I seldom feel so close to god as when I am being whipped for mine own wickedness, though my darkest sins are no wise near as black as his.\'94 
\par \'93B-but,\'94 she sputtered, \'93you preach the Mother\rquote s mercy . . .\'94 
